build I20041116

- shortly after starting up on the new build, I pressed Ctrl+Shift+W to close
all editors
- one of the .class file editors failed to be materialized due to changes in the
classpath (first two entries in the log below)
- this then caused an NPE in PresentablePartFolder.internalRemove (last entry)

Also, it looks as if the close all is causing the editors being removed to be
materialized.  If the editor was not already materialized, then it should not be
materialized just to close it.
